    <div class="submitted active">Submitted by <a href="/user/48427" title="View user profile.">befree</a> on Sat, 10/06/2012 - 19:01.  <a class="permalink" href="/comment/2776391">Permalink</a></div>
	<div class="content">
     <p>They don't give enough numbers to tell what is really going on.  However, they do give enough to slant it to try to make you think they don't have enough police.  </p>
